name: Intel x JP the Money Bear

metadata.name: Intel x JP the Money Bear 1
metadata.description: Intel x JP the Money Bear NFT by world renowned contemporary artist King Saladeen, created using an Intel Evo laptop. This JP the Money Bear is wearing an Intel Evo utility vest, and has a wifi symbol in one eye to symbolize the lightning fast internet speeds of Intel Evo laptops, and his signature money symbol in the other eye.
